  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb4\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0baf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4 \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Anti-Terrorism Act on University Students",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Dines Gunawardena has said that the Anti-Terrorism Act will not be used against the arrested university students.",
        "The Prime Minister said this while replying to a question raised by Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasa in Parliament today. (R)"
      ],
